dc_title_s: 32,000 to vote in 29 precincts here: [Bloomington, Ind.].
dc_description_s: From Daily Herald-Telephone, Bloomington, Indiana, November 4, 1966.; Map shows voting precincts inside the City of Bloomington, Indiana, and includes listing of polling places inside the city (shown on map) and outside the City of Bloomington in Monroe County, Indiana (not shown on map). Scale not given.
